rComments: She really seemed to care about what she was teaching, but she went on and on about the same subject every class. She didn't make it easy to know what she wanted in the written assignments we were assigned.
I loved the material taught by prof Brahim this semester and generally enjoyed the class. The lectures were often boring, but it was still an easy pass if you read the material.

Prof. Brahim est très organisée et disponible pour répondre aux questions. Les évaluations sont très faciles. Les critères d'évaluation sont explicites et donne beaucoup d'exemples de travaux pour donner une idée de ce qui est demandé. Revient souvent sur les mêmes idées cours après cours, mais le FRA1710 est bâti de cette façon...

She is for sure one of the most genuine and sincere profs I've ever had! 2 books to read (around 200 pages), 2 grammar tests, 2 reading tests and 2 papers to write (around 300 words). I know it seems like a lot but it really isn't, the tests are short and so are the books. Definitely would take it again she's such a sweetheart!!
